# ⚡️ Type: Brief description (max 50 chars)
#
# Explain what and why vs. how
# Use the imperative mood: "Add feature" not "Added feature"
# Capitalize the subject line
# Do not end the subject line with a period
# 
# Types:
# ✨ feat: New feature
# 🐛 fix: Bug fix
# 📚 docs: Documentation changes
# 🎨 style: Code style changes (formatting, missing semicolons, etc.)
# ♻️ refactor: Code refactoring
# ⚡️ perf: Performance improvements
# ✅ test: Adding or updating tests
# 🔧 chore: Build process or auxiliary tool changes
# 🔥 remove: Remove code or files
# 🚀 deploy: Deployment related changes
#
# Examples:
# ✨ feat: Add web push notifications
# 🐛 fix: Resolve chapter download timeout issue
# 📚 docs: Update README with push notification setup
# ♻️ refactor: Extract EPUB generation to separate module
